title: Blind Faith - 1969-08-16 - Fairgrounds Arena
description:
Here is another nice bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Blind Faith 08/16/69
Earl Warren Showgrounds
Santa Barbara

CA , FM ?, SBD ?, from reel to reel source. 
 
1. Announcement
2. Well Allright
3. Can't Find My Way Home
4. Had To Cry Today
5. Sleeping In The Ground (jump in)(1 glitch)
6. Crossroads
7. Presence Of The Lord
8. Means To An End
9. Do What You Like (jump in on the 1st note) > Jam > (1 drop between track 9 & 10)
10. Drums Solo > Do What You Like > Band Intro (1 drop)
 
Something about this show :
I got this 25 years ago and on my reel to reel box i have soundboard recording...i think this is not a SBD, but a FM or great audience recording, by the way, recording is really good. Both the date and venue of this show have been disputed. It would appear that no concert occurred at this venue or on this date. On the other side this is not likely any other performance or date i have, so any help to find out the truth is more than welcome.
